│Staging key lost                                        │
│                                                        │
│The staging data key could not be recovered from the    │
│keychain, so every staged change for this scope is      │
│unreadable and must be re-created from scratch after    │
│clearing the store. Check that the login keychain is    │
│unlocked, that no other process holds it, and that      │
│SUVE_STAGING_KEY is either unset or matches the key the │
│store was written with. If the keychain entry was       │
│deleted, the staged changes cannot be recovered and the │
│store must be reset before staging again from this      │
│scope. Re-run the command after unlocking the keychain  │
│                                                        │
│↑↓/pgup/pgdn: scroll · enter/esc: close                 │
╰────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯